Strategic Objectives

  • SO1

    Timely, multi-sectoral, life-saving, equitable and safe assistance is provided to crisis-affected people of all genders and diversities to reduce mortality and morbidity.

  • SO2

    Protection risks are mitigated, while protection and human rights needs for people of all genders and diversities are monitored and addressed through integrated and inclusive humanitarian action.

  • SO3

    Vulnerable people of all gender and diversities are supported to build their resilience and live their lives in dignity.
